ржПрж╕ржмрзЗрж░ рж╕рж╛ржерзЗ Suspense automatically ржХрж╛ржЬ ржХрж░рзЗ
ЁЯФ╣ Basic Syntax
import { Suspense } from "react";

<Suspense fallback={<p>Loading...</p>}>
  <MyComponent />
</Suspense>


ЁЯУМ fallback тЖТ ржпрждржХрзНрж╖ржг MyComponent рж▓рзЛржб рж╣ржЪрзНржЫрзЗ, ржПржЯрж╛ ржжрзЗржЦрж╛ржмрзЗ
ЁЯФ╣ Next.js (App Router) Example
ЁЯУБ app/page.jsx
import { Suspense } from "react";
import Users from "./Users";

export default function Page() {
  return (
    <div>
      <h1>User List</h1>

      <Suspense fallback={<p>Loading users...</p>}>
        <Users />
      </Suspense>
    </div>
  );
}

ЁЯУБ app/Users.jsx (Server Component)
async function getUsers() {
  await new Promise((r) => setTimeout(r, 2000)); // fake delay
  return ["Rahim", "Karim", "Hasan"];
}

export default async function Users() {
  const users = await getUsers();

  return (
    <ul>
      {users.map((u) => (
        <li key={u}>{u}</li>
      ))}
    </ul>
  );
}


ЁЯЯв ржПржЦрж╛ржирзЗ:

Users load рж╣рждрзЗ 2 рж╕рзЗржХрзЗржирзНржб рж▓рж╛ржЧржЫрзЗ

рж╕рзЗржЗ рж╕ржорзЯ Loading users... ржжрзЗржЦрж╛ржмрзЗ

ЁЯФ╣ Suspense + Dynamic Component
import dynamic from "next/dynamic";

const HeavyComponent = dynamic(() => import("./HeavyComponent"), {
  suspense: true,
});

<Suspense fallback={<p>Loading heavy part...</p>}>
  <HeavyComponent />
</Suspense>

ЁЯФ╣ Suspense vs loading.js (Next.js)
ржмрж┐рж╖рзЯ	Suspense	loading.js
Scope	Component level	Route level
Control	ржмрзЗрж╢рж┐	ржХржо
Streaming	тЬЕ	тЬЕ

ЁЯУМ Best Practice:

Page/Route loading тЖТ loading.js

Specific component тЖТ Suspense

ЁЯФ╣ Multiple Suspense (Advanced)
<Suspense fallback={<HeaderSkeleton />}>
  <Header />
</Suspense>

<Suspense fallback={<PostsSkeleton />}>
  <Posts />
</Suspense>


ЁЯСЙ Header ржЖржЧрзЗ ржжрзЗржЦрж╛ржмрзЗ, Posts ржкрж░рзЗ ржЖрж╕ржмрзЗ

